INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1,1,'Конспект. Как писать понятный и красивый код?','<div class=\"tm-article-presenter__meta\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; box-sizing: border-box; color: #548eaa; font-size: medium; line-height: 28.8px; margin: 24px 0px; max-width: 780px; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"tm-article-body\" lang=\"ru\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; box-sizing: border-box; padding-top: 16px; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-gallery-root=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"post-content-body\" class=\"article-formatted-body article-formatted-body_version-1\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #111111; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.56; overflow-wrap: break-word; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\r\n<div style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Глава 1. Чистый код</h3>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Что же такое этот самый чистый код по версии Мартина в нескольких словах? Это код без дублирования, с минимальным количеством сущностей, удобный для чтения, простой. В качестве девиза можно было бы выбрать: &laquo;Ясность превыше всего!&raquo;.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Глава 2. Содержательные имена</h3>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Имена должны передавать намерения программиста</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Имя переменной, функции или класса должно сообщить, почему эта переменная существует, что она делает и как используется. Если имя требует дополнительных комментариев, значит, оно не передает намерений программиста. Лучше написать, что именно измеряется и в каких именно единицах.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Пример хорошего названия переменной: daysSinceCreation;<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Цель: убрать неочевидность.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Избегайте дезинформации</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Не используйте слова со скрытыми значениями, отличными от предполагаемого. Остерегайтесь малозаметных различий в именах. Например, XYZControllerForEfficientHandlingOfStrings и XYZControllerForEfficientStorageOfStrings.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />По-настоящему устрашающие примеры дезинформирующих имен встречаются при использовании строчной &laquo;L&raquo; и прописной &laquo;O&raquo; в именах переменных, особенно в комбинациях. Естественно, проблемы возникают из-за того, что эти буквы почти не отличаются от констант &laquo;1&raquo; и &laquo;0&raquo; соответственно.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Используйте осмысленные различия</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Если имена различаются, то они должны обозначать разные понятия.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />&laquo;Числовые ряды&raquo; вида (a1, a2,&hellip; aN) являются противоположностью сознательного присваивания имен. Они не несут информации и не дают представления о намерениях автора.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Неинформативные слова избыточны. Слово variable никогда не должно встречаться в именах переменных. Слово table никогда не должно встречаться в именах таблиц. Чем имя NameString лучше Name? Разве имя может быть, скажем, вещественным числом?<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Используйте удобопроизносимые имена: generationTimestamp намного лучше genymdhms.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Выбирайте имена, удобные для поиска</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Однобуквенные имена могут использоваться только для локальных переменных в коротких методах.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Избегайте схем кодирования имен</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Как правило, кодированные имена плохо произносятся и в них легко сделать опечатку.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Интерфейсы и реализации</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Я (автор книги) предпочитаю оставлять имена интерфейсов без префиксов. Префикс I, столь распространенный в старом коде, в лучшем случае отвлекает, а в худшем &mdash; передает лишнюю информацию. Я не собираюсь сообщать своим пользователям, что они имеют дело с интерфейсом.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Имена классов</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Имена классов и объектов должны представлять собой существительные и их комбинации: Customer, WikiPage, Account и AddressParser. Старайтесь не использовать в именах классов такие слова, как Manager, Processor, Data или Info. Имя класса не должно быть глаголом.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Имена методов</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Имена методов представляют собой глаголы или глагольные словосочетания: postPayment, deletePage, save и т. д. Методы чтения/записи и предикаты образуются из значения и префикса get, set и is согласно стандарту javabean.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Воздержитесь от каламбуров</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Задача автора &mdash; сделать свой код как можно более понятным. Код должен восприниматься с первого взгляда, не требуя тщательного изучения. Ориентируйтесь на модель популярной литературы, в которой сам автор должен доступно выразить свои мысли.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Добавьте содержательный контекст</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Контекст можно добавить при помощи префиксов: addrFirstName, addrLastName, addrState и т. д. По крайней мере читатель кода поймет, что переменные являются частью более крупной структуры. Конечно, правильнее было бы создать класс с именем Address, чтобы даже компилятор знал, что переменные являются частью чего-то большего.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Переменные с неясным контекстом:<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<pre style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; background: #fbfdff; border: 1px solid #e5e8ec; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 17px 20px; tab-size: 4; white-space: pre; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code class=\"java hljs\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: inherit; background: none; color: #4d4d4c; display: block; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: normal; white-space: pre; tab-size: 4; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">printGuessStatistics</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">char</span> candidate, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">int</span> count)</span> </span>{\r\n    String number;\r\n    String verb;\r\n    String pluralModifier;\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">if</span> (count == <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">0</span>) {\r\n      number = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"no\"</span>;\r\n      verb = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"are\"</span>;\r\n      pluralModifier = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"s\"</span>;\r\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">else</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">if</span> (count == <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">1</span>) {\r\n      number = ~_~quotquot~_~;\r\n      verb = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"is\"</span>;\r\n      pluralModifier = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"\"</span>;\r\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">else</span> {\r\n      number = Integer.toString(count);\r\n      verb = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"are\"</span>;\r\n      pluralModifier = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"s\"</span>;\r\n    }\r\n    String guessMessage = String.format(\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"There %s %s %s%s\"</span>, verb, number, candidate, pluralModifier\r\n    );\r\n    print(guessMessage);\r\n  }\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Функция длинновата, а переменные используются на всем ее протяжении. Чтобы разделить функцию на меньшие смысловые фрагменты, следует создать класс GuessStatisticsMessage и сделать три переменные полями этого класса. Тем самым мы предоставим очевидный контекст для трех переменных &mdash; теперь абсолютно очевидно, что эти переменные являются частью GuessStatisticsMessage.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Переменные с контекстом:<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<pre style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; background: #fbfdff; border: 1px solid #e5e8ec; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 17px 20px; tab-size: 4; white-space: pre; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code class=\"java hljs\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: inherit; background: none; color: #4d4d4c; display: block; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: normal; white-space: pre; tab-size: 4; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">GuessStatisticsMessage</span> </span>{\r\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0