 -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">thereAreNoLetters</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">()</span> </span>{\r\n    number = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"no\"</span>;\r\n    verb = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"are\"</span>;\r\n    pluralModifier = <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #718c00; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">\"s\"</span>;\r\n  }\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Не добавляйте избыточный контекст</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Короткие имена обычно лучше длинных, если только их смысл понятен читателю кода. Не включайте в имя больше контекста, чем необходимо.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Глава 3. Функции</h3>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Компактность!</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Первое правило: функции должны быть компактными.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Второе правило: функции должны быть еще компактнее.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Мой практический опыт научил меня (ценой многих проб и ошибок), что функции должны быть очень маленькими. Желательно, чтобы длина функции не превышала 20 строк.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Правило одной операции</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Функция должна выполнять только одну операцию. Она должна выполнять ее хорошо. И ничего другого она делать не должна. Если функция выполняет только те действия, которые находятся на одном уровне под объявленным именем функции, то эта функция выполняет одну операцию.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Секции в функциях</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Функцию, выполняющую только одну операцию, невозможно осмысленно разделить на секции.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Один уровень абстракции на функцию</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Чтобы убедиться в том, что функция выполняет &laquo;только одну операцию&raquo;, необходимо проверить, что все команды функции находятся на одном уровне абстракции.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Смешение уровней абстракции внутри функции всегда создает путаницу.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Чтение кода сверху вниз: правило понижения</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Код должен читаться как рассказ &mdash; сверху вниз.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />За каждой функцией должны следовать функции следующего уровня абстракции. Это позволяет читать код, последовательно спускаясь по уровням абстракции в ходе чтения списка функций. Я называю такой подход &laquo;правилом понижения&raquo;.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Команды switch</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Написать компактную команду switch довольно сложно. Даже команда switch всего с двумя условиями занимает больше места, чем в моем представлении должен занимать один блок или функция. Также трудно создать команду switch, которая делает что-то одно &mdash; по своей природе команды switch всегда выполняют N операций. К сожалению, обойтись без команд switch удается не всегда, но по крайней мере мы можем позаботиться о том, чтобы эти команды были скрыты в низкоуровневом классе и не дублировались в коде. И конечно, в этом нам может помочь полиморфизм.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />В примере представлена всего одна операция, зависящая от типа работника.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<pre style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; background: #fbfdff; border: 1px solid #e5e8ec; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 17px 20px; tab-size: 4; white-space: pre; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code class=\"java hljs\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: inherit; background: none; color: #4d4d4c; display: block; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: normal; white-space: pre; tab-size: 4; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> Money <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">calculatePay</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">(Employee e)</span> \r\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">throws</span> InvalidEmployeeType </span>{\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">switch</span> (e.type) {\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">case</span> COMMISSIONED:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">return</span> calculateCommissionedPay(e);\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">case</span> HOURLY:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">return</span> calculateHourlyPay(e);\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">case</span> SALARIED:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">return</span> calculateSalariedPay(e);\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">default</span>:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">throw</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">new</span> InvalidEmployeeType(e.type);\r\n    }\r\n  }</code></pre>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Эта функция имеет ряд недостатков. Во-первых, она велика, а при добавлении новых типов работников она будет разрастаться. Во-вторых, она совершенно очевидно выполняет более одной операции. В-третьих, она нарушает принцип единой ответственности (Single responsibility principle), так как у нее существует несколько возможных причин изменения.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />В-четвертых, она нарушает принцип открытости/закрытости (The Open Closed Principle), потому что код функции должен изменяться при каждом добавлении новых типов.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Но, пожалуй, самый серьезный недостаток заключается в том, что программа может содержать неограниченное количество других функций с аналогичной структурой, например:<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />isPayday(Employee e, Date date)<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />или<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />deliverPay(Employee e, Money pay)<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />и так далее.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Все эти функции будут иметь все ту же ущербную структуру. Решение проблемы заключается в том, чтобы похоронить команду switch в фундаменте абстрактной фабрики и никому ее не показывать. Фабрика использует команду switch для создания соответствующих экземпляров потомков Employee, а вызовы функций calculatePay, isPayDay, deliverPay и т. д. проходят полиморфную передачу через интерфейс Employee.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<pre style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; background: #fbfdff; border: 1px solid #e5e8ec; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 17px 20px; tab-size: 4; white-space: pre; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code class=\"java hljs\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: inherit; background: none; color: #4d4d4c; display: block; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: normal; white-space: pre; tab-size: 4; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">abstract</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">Employee</span> </span>{\r\n  <span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">abstract</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">boolean</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">isPayday</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">()</span></span>;\r\n  <span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">abstract</span> Money <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">calculatePay</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">()</span></span>;\r\n  <span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">abstract</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">deliverPay</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">(Money pay)</span></span>;\r\n}\r\n-----------------\r\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">interface</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">EmployeeFactory</span> </span>{\r\n  <span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> Employee <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">makeEmployee</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">(EmployeeRecord r)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">throws</span> InvalidEmployeeType</span>;\r\n}\r\n-----------------\r\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">EmployeeFactoryImpl</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">implements</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">EmployeeFactory</span> </span>{\r\n  <span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">public</span> Employee <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">makeEmployee</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">(EmployeeRecord r)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">throws</span> InvalidEmployeeType </span>{\r\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">switch</span> (r.type) {\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">case</span> COMMISSIONED:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">new</span> CommissionedEmployee(r) ;\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">case</span> HOURLY:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">new</span> HourlyEmployee(r);\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">case</span> SALARIED:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">new</span> SalariedEmploye(r);\r\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">default</span>:\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">throw</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">new</span> InvalidEmployeeType(r.type);\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Мое общее правило в отношении команд switch гласит, что эти команды допустимы, если они встречаются в программе однократно, используются для создания полиморфных объектов и скрываются за отношениями наследования, чтобы оставаться невидимыми для остальных частей системы. Конечно, правил без исключений не бывает и в некоторых ситуациях приходится нарушать одно или несколько условий этого правила.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Используйте содержательные имена</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Половина усилий по реализации этого принципа сводится к выбору хороших имен для компактных функций, выполняющих одну операцию. Чем меньше и специализированнее функция, тем проще выбрать для нее содержательное имя.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Не бойтесь использовать длинные имена Длинное содержательное имя лучше короткого невразумительного. Выберите схему, которая позволяет легко прочитать слова в имени функции, а затем составьте из этих слов имя, которое описывает назначение функции.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Аргументы функций</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />В идеальном случае количество аргументов функции равно нулю. Далее следуют функции с одним аргументом (унарные) и с двумя аргументами (бинарные). Функций с тремя аргументами (тернарных) следует по возможности избегать.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Выходные аргументы запутывают ситуацию еще быстрее, чем входные. Как правило, никто не ожидает, что функция будет возвращать информацию в аргументах. Если уж обойтись без аргументов никак не удается, постарайтесь хотя бы ограничиться одним входным аргументом.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Преобразования, в которых вместо возвращаемого значения используется выходной аргумент, сбивают читателя с толку. Если функция преобразует свой входной аргумент, то результат<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />должен передаваться в возвращаемом значении.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Аргументы-флаги</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Аргументы-флаги уродливы. Передача логического значения функции &mdash; воистину ужасная привычка. Она немедленно усложняет сигнатуру метода, громко провозглашая, что функция выполняет более одной операции. При истинном значении флага выполняется одна операция, а при ложном &mdash; другая.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Бинарные функции</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Функцию с двумя аргументами понять сложнее, чем унарную функцию. Конечно, в некоторых ситуациях форма с двумя аргументами оказывается уместной. Например, вызов Point p = new Point(0,0); абсолютно разумен. Однако два аргумента в нашем случае являются упорядоченными компонентами одного значения.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Объекты как аргументы</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Если функция должна получать более двух или трех аргументов, весьма вероятно, что некоторые из этих аргументов стоит упаковать в отдельном классе. Рассмотрим следующие два объявления:<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<pre style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: monospace, monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; background: #fbfdff; border: 1px solid #e5e8ec; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px; overflow: auto; padding: 17px 20px; tab-size: 4; white-space: pre; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code class=\"java hljs\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Courier New\', Courier, monospace; font-size: inherit; background: none; color: #4d4d4c; display: block; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0px; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; border-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: normal; white-space: pre; tab-size: 4; word-break: normal; word-spacing: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">Circle <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">makeCircle</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">double</span> x, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">double</span> y, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">double</span> radius)</span></span>;\r\n<span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">Circle <span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #4271ae; font-weight: bold; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">makeCircle</span><span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: #f5871f; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">(Point center, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; font-weight: bold; color: #8959a8; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\">double</span> radius)</span></span>; </code></pre>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Если переменные передаются совместно как единое целое (как переменные x и y в этом примере), то, скорее всего, вместе они образуют концепцию, заслуживающую собственного имени.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Глаголы и ключевые слова</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Выбор хорошего имени для функции способен в значительной мере объяснить смысл функции, а также порядок и смысл ее аргументов. В унарных функциях сама функция и ее аргумент должны образовывать естественную пару &laquo;глагол/существительное&raquo;. Например, вызов вида write(name) смотрится весьма информативно.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Читатель понимает, что чем бы ни было &laquo;имя&raquo; (name), оно куда-то &laquo;записывается&raquo; (write). Еще лучше запись writeField(name), которая сообщает, что &laquo;имя&raquo; записывается в &laquo;поле&raquo; какой-то структуры.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Последняя запись является примером использования ключевых слов в имени функции. В этой форме имена аргументов кодируются в имени функции. Например, assertEquals можно записать в виде assertExpectedEqualsActual(expected, actual). Это в значительной мере решает проблему запоминания порядка аргументов.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Разделение команд и запросов</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Функция должна что-то делать или отвечать на какой-то вопрос, но не одновременно. Либо функция изменяет состояние объекта, либо возвращает информацию об этом объекте. Совмещение двух операций часто создает путаницу.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Изолируйте блоки try/catch</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Блоки try/catch выглядят весьма уродливо. Они запутывают структуру кода и смешивают обработку ошибок с нормальной обработкой. По этой причине тела блоков try и catch рекомендуется выделять в отдельные функции.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />\r\n<h4 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Обработка ошибок как одна операция</h4>\r\n<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Функции должны выполнять одну операцию. Обработка ошибок &mdash; это одна операция. Значит, функция, обрабатывающая ошибки, ничего другого делать не должна. Отсюда следует, что если в функции присутствует ключевое слово try, то оно должно быть первым словом в функции, а после блоков catch/finally ничего другого быть не должно.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />На этом глава 3 заканчивается.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','/uploads/efiygknwshp6q_5wtna1q_dewti.jpeg'),(2,1,'Программист-фанатик. Как сохранить конкурентные преимущества и стать заметным?','<p><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">У Фаулера часто совершенно не отражающие сути названия глав. Раньше я оставлял название как есть. Но цель конспекта передать смысл, а, как уже сказал, названия часто его не несут. Поэтому я буду писать в названии глав основную идею совета. Повторять в тексте я ее уже не буду, ведь, эта идея озвучена.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.625rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Часть 4</h2>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Как мне недавно сказал один начальник, если кто-то делает нечто совершенно фантастическое, но об этом никто не знает, можно считать, что он не делает ничего.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Это глава посвящена раскрытию тезиса &laquo;Нужно быть заметным&raquo; и способам как этого добиться.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 33. Чужое мнение &mdash; важно</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Фаулер советует составить таблицу репутации и развиваться по этим направлениям</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><img style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; border-style: none; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; color: #7e6e6f; font-size: 0.75rem; font-style: italic; cursor: pointer; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" src=\"https://habrastorage.org/r/w1560/webt/ns/pp/jd/nsppjdldr9oxpoxc2n8sfpgp6bw.jpeg\" data-src=\"https://habrastorage.org/webt/ns/pp/jd/nsppjdldr9oxpoxc2n8sfpgp6bw.jpeg\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 34. Будь приятным</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Для клиента ты должен стать проводником по суровым землям мира информационных технологий.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">К склочному, раздражительному и неприятному человеку плохо относятся.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 35. Грамотность и последовательность структуры объяснений</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Ежедневно делай короткие записи, объясняя, над чем ты работаешь, обосновывая собственные проекты и подвергая тщательной проверке технические или профессиональные решения.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 36. Личное общение важно</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Выдели один день на следующей неделе и постарайся (в разумных пределах) обойтись без электронной почты.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 37. Разработка решает цели бизнеса</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Разработчику программного обеспечения необходимо строить рассказ о своих достижениях, учитывая бизнес, на который он работает.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Хорошо, ты это сделал, но что это вообще такое? Почему оно имеет значение? Докажи, что это так называемое достижение не является для компании потерей времени.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Перечисли свои недавние достижения. Напиши, какую выгоду бизнесу принесло каждое из них.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 38. Глобальная цель</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Для отличия от других и заметности Фаулер предлагает продвигать какую-либо глобальную идею. Это позволяет стать заметнее.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 39. Выступать на конференциях</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 40. Создать личный бренд</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Поищи информацию о себе в Google. Введи в строку поиска собственное имя в кавычках. Посмотри первые четыре страницы результатов (если их наберется четыре страницы). Что может подумать о тебе человек, просмотревший только ссылки с этих четырех страниц?</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 41. Работать над open source проектами</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Работа над программами с открытым исходным кодом не только дает возможность создать себе имя, но и демонстрирует твою увлеченность данной областью деятельности.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 42. Написать книгу</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 43. Много знакомиться и общаться</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Напиши письмо автору своей любимой программы.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.625rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Часть 5</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 44. Технологии быстро устаревают</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Каждую неделю выделяй время на знакомство с передовыми технологиями.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 45. Профессии устаревают и меняются</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Тут Фаулер говорит, что мир очень быстро меняется и нужно быть готовым пойти работать в другую профессию. Откровенно говоря, такой себе совет. Сначала стать &laquo;программистом-фанатиком&raquo;, а потом отказаться от профессии&hellip;</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 46. Путь к цели и есть сама цель</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Цель разработки программного обеспечения &mdash; момент передачи заказчику готового кода. Ему требуется приложение, и ты концентрируешься на том, чтобы его создать.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Но при этом приложение никогда не будет полностью готовым. Одна версия тянет за собой другую.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Слишком сильная концентрация на конечном продукте отвлекает нас от реальной деятельности: непрекращающейся работы над новой программой.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 47. Составить план карьеры</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Перед тем как строить планы на будущее, стоит описать свое текущее положение. Составь хронологию своей карьеры.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Покажи, с чего ты начал, какие навыки и рабочие обязанности требовались на каждом этапе. Обрати внимание, когда происходили постепенные улучшения, а когда совершался большой скачок вперед.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Определи промежуток времени, за который произошло твое главное повышение. Используй эту информацию в качестве базиса и строй дальнейшую карьеру. Четкая картина пройденного пути позволяет ставить более реалистичные цели.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Постоянно обновляй план. Это замечательный способ продемонстрировать собственные достижения по мере движения к новым намеченным целям.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 48. Следить за изменениями</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Мир постоянно меняется и нужно внимательно следить за любыми изменениями окружающей среды, чтобы ничего не пропустить и не оказаться за бортом.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 49. Никто не видит себя со стороны</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Воспользуйся методом 360-градусной оценки:</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<ol style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; padding-inline-start: 32px; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px;\">Составь список заслуживающих доверие лиц, мнением которых ты можешь поинтересоваться, не испытывая дискомфорта. В список должны попасть представители разных групп: коллеги, заказчики, руководители (и подчиненные, если они у тебя есть) .</li>\r\n<li style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; line-height: 1.6; margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px;\">Перечисли десять характеристик, которые являются мерами твоего профессионализма (с твоей точки зрения) .</li>\r\n<li style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; line-height: 1.6; margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px;\">Преврати список в опросный лист. Попроси участников дать тебе оценкув терминах каждой из характеристик. Включи туда вопрос &laquo;О чем еще мне следовало спросить?&raquo;</li>\r\n<li style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; line-height: 1.6; margin: 6px 0px 0px; padding: 0px;\">Раздай опросные листы людям, список которых ты составил на первом этапе. Попроси дать честные отзывы, тебе не нужна приукрашенная действительность .</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 50. Гибкость во взглядах</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Фаулер советует такую методику:</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Назови свои жесткие критерии. Какие ценности, о которых ты даже не задумываешься, управляют твоими ежедневными действиями?</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Нарисуй таблицу с двумя столбцами: &laquo;карьера&raquo; и &laquo;технология&raquo;.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">В каждом столбце перечисли ценности, которые ты считаешь непоколебимо верными.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">К примеру, в столбце &laquo;карьера&raquo; укажи характеристики, которые всегда считал своими сильными сторонами.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Перечисли и то, что считаешь своими слабостями.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">А как насчет карьерных устремлений? (&laquo;Я хочу стать генеральным директором!&raquo;). Укажи правильные пути достижения цели.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">В столбце &laquo;технология&raquo; перечисли, что ты считаешь самым ценным в технологиях, в которые решил вложиться. Какие наиболее важные атрибуты технологии следует учитывать в процессе выбора? Каким образом ты создаешь масштабируемые системы?</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Какой видишь наиболее продуктивную среду для разработки программного обеспечения? Какие платформы лучше, а какие хуже всего в общем случае?</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Завершив работу над списком, начни его перечитывать и для каждого пункта мысленно формируй противоположное утверждение. Ты допускаешь, что противоположный взгляд на вещи тоже может быть верным? Попробуй честно оценить каждую из записанных тобой характеристик.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 51. Гибкое планирование карьеры</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Ставь большие цели, но по пути постоянно вноси в них коррективы.</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 52. Принцип &laquo;лучше, чем вчера&raquo;</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Масштабные цели лишают мотивации.</span><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><em style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Секрет в попытках сделать так, чтобы задача, над которой ты работаешь, сегодня стала лучше, чем вчера. Вот и все. Это легко.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />Составь список сложных или трудно достижимых целей. Подумай над каждым пунктом, что ты можешь сделать, чтобы уже сегодня стать лучше, чем вчера.<br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\';\" />На следующий день снова перечитай список. Был ли вчерашний день лучше, чем позавчерашний? Как сегодня еще заметнее улучшить свои показатели?</em><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.4375rem; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: \'Fira Sans\', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #111111; background-color: #ffffff;\">Совет 53. Фриланс делает более ответственным</h3>\r\n<p><br style=\"transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out 0s, -webkit-text-decoration 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; quotes: \'&laquo;\' \'&raquo;\'; color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">На этом книга заканчивается. Фаулер иногда спорен, иногда интересен а иногда играет роль капитана очевидность. В любом случае каждый может найти над чем поразмыслить и извлечь что-то полезное для себя.</span></p>','/uploads/_mabd44gsqh6q1uwwsvt2_tcuye.jpeg');
